aWFQuestionnaireDesc.Content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="ISO-8859-1" ?> <Questionnaire> <Field Kind="Boolean"> <Id>Q1</Id> <Title> <Value>Has any person applying for coverage been advised or recommended by a physician to have surgery which has not yet been performed?</Value> <Presentor>Title Auto</Presentor> <Font> <FontName>MS Sans Serif</FontName> <FontSize>8</FontSize> <FontSels></FontSels> </Font> </Title> <VisibilityRule></VisibilityRule> <ValueInformation> <IsMandatory>Yes</IsMandatory> <Presentor>In Line</Presentor> <Value>No</Value> </ValueInformation> </Field> <Field Kind="Boolean"> <Id>Q2</Id> <Title> <Value>Is any person applying for coverage currently disabled or does any person applying for coverage have a condition which prevents or limits activities?</Value> <Presentor>Title Auto</Presentor> <Font> <FontName>MS Sans Serif</FontName> <FontSize>8</FontSize> <FontSels></FontSels> </Font> </Title> <VisibilityRule></VisibilityRule> <ValueInformation> <IsMandatory>Yes</IsMandatory> <Presentor>In Line</Presentor> <Value>No</Value> </ValueInformation> </Field> </Questionnaire>
